                    <span>If you are a system administrator, like I am, you will appreciate sample VBScript-based scripts presented in this book. This is what has been missing from any Microsoft WMI documentation (including their Software Development Kit). And finally the publisher (SAMS) decided to post the source code on their web site.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Great book -- Well done...</div>
