                    <span>This book is very timely, extremely accurate, and in complete touch with the latest management technologies offered on Windows computers. Marcin does a great job relating each topic and the scripts run flawlessly. BIG TIP (but thoroughly logical): Make sure you have the latest versions of both WMI and Windows Script Host/VB Script installed on your computer when playing with the scripts. ... </span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Okay... With qualifications</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
